Maintainer: Serge Balandine <serge.balandine@epicentre.msf.org>
Description: A Shiny application for geospatial sampling of building
    structures within defined polygon areas. Supports quadrat, T-square,
    and random sampling methods with OpenStreetMap and Google satellite
    imagery integration for field epidemiology surveys.
